    SeqClass -->|loads| HFSeqClass
    AutoFinder -->|discovers| TGISClient

    HTTPServer -->|routes to| TextGen
    HTTPServer -->|routes to| Embedding
    HTTPServer -->|routes to| Classification
    HTTPServer -->|routes to| Tokenization
    GRPCServer -->|routes to| TextGen
    GRPCServer -->|routes to| Embedding
    GRPCServer -->|routes to| Classification
    GRPCServer -->|routes to| Tokenization

    %% External interactions
    Client[Client / API Consumer] -->|HTTP POST| HTTPServer
    Client -->|gRPC| GRPCServer

    KServe[KServe Gateway] -->|routes to| HTTPServer
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh] -->|routes to| GRPCServer

    TGISClient -->|gRPC<br/>Configurable mTLS| TGIS[TGIS Backend<br/>caikit-tgis-serving]
    EmbMod -->|in-process| STModels[sentence-transformers<br/>Local Models]
    CrossEnc -->|in-process| STModels

    HFCausalLM -.->|optional download<br/>HTTPS/443| HFHub[HuggingFace Hub]

